//“Crystal Engraved Crushed Opal Ring” in @glassalchemy “Terps”//✨sold DM for custom inquiries
I was recently asked for a ring with “Maximum Opal”, here’s what I came up with! 🙌💎✨ Being one of my birthstones, Opal is personally one of my favorite materials to work with and this ring really speaks to that... absolutely love the way the Black Opal refract and compliment the “Terps” on this piece, much love as always to the #OpalPlug @grandpaglass!!
💎💎💎
SWIPE LEFT for detail shots
This ring features some @grandpaglass “Wizard blend” crushed Opal prepped in @glassalchemy “Terps” by the shopmate and homie @truchalkglass, all rung up in a fully #freehandfaceted cut, polish, and engraving as well as 16 @grandpaglass Black Opal Inlays shining and refracting throughout the band... be sure to check out the videos above and swipe left for CFL and detail shots!
💎💎💎
This ring is #sold to longtime collector #VINHWINHcollector @stoneybolognawithcheese, thanks for the support homie! If anyone is interested in a similar custom feel free to DM me for inquiries... these rings are a true labor of love and I am stoked to have them in every glass collection I can, thanks so much for the support in letting me do what I do all! 🙌❣️✨
